<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="//p4.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201125/561f61c3ad8c4d7980a5bf688feb8fe4.jpeg" width="530" /></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>阿科斯塔推特截图</span></p>
